    StructureDefinition-contained-p

    source file: source/pages/_includes/contained-p-intro.md

    The Open mHealth Contained Patient Profile defines the minimum expectations for the using a contained Patient resource within the Open mHealth DocumentReference profile to represent an opaque patient identifier.

    Formal Views of Profile Content

    Description of Profiles, Differentials, and Snapshots.

    The official URL for this profile is: http://www.fhir.org/guides/omhtofhir/StructureDefinition/contained-p

    Published on Fri Nov 23 00:00:00 PST 2018 as active by the Open mHealth.

    This profile builds on Patient

    Mandatory: 3 elements

    system S0..1uriThe namespace for the identifier value
    value S1..1stringThe value that is unique
